elements.name: buyRate
elements.expression: buyRate = minRate.mul(FEE_MULTIPLIER * RATE_MULTIPLIER - buyFee * RATE_MULTIPLIER / 100) / FEE_MULTIPLIER / RATE_MULTIPLIER

elements.name: sellRate
elements.expression: sellRate = maxRate.mul(FEE_MULTIPLIER * RATE_MULTIPLIER + sellFee * RATE_MULTIPLIER / 100) / FEE_MULTIPLIER / RATE_MULTIPLIER
